  "synopsis": "Among the treasures from the Immortal Manor, Qin Yu, along with venturers from other sects, find clues relating to the Ni Yang Realm, a realm of the Immortal Emperor Ni Yang. When Jiang Li is forced to return home, Jiang Lan decides to go back for her. Before leaving, he gives a parting gift to Qin Yu, one that may help him meet her. Setting out to the Ni Yang Realm, Qin Yu faces various ordeals before he gains knowledge on the strength he will be needing in order to meet Jiang Li again.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]",
